        <info>&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Learn about and contact your new lead quickly. Gather as much contact information as you can.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: HelveticaNeue; font-size: 9.75pt;&quot;&gt;Get your lead’s email address, phone number, and title so that you can include your lead in future campaigns.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: HelveticaNeue; font-size: 9.75pt;&quot;&gt;Email your lead first, and immediately follow up with a phone call.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;Stage Completion Criteria: You have attempted to contact your Lead.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</info>
