        <info>&lt;p&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 9.75pt; font-family: HelveticaNeue;&quot;&gt;Congratulations! &lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;Now it’s time to convert the lead record to an opportunity.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</info>
